From f37d2a668fd82c408b87a4520fb3711203cea606 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: fi3 <email@email.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 08:07:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] ADD selected-agent backend command routing so slash
 commands bypass normal prompts

Route selected slash-prefixed chat input through the active provider command hook so backend commands use the existing session thread without being rewritten as ordinary prompts. Keep unsupported providers source-compatible with default command replies, and document the provider contract because the command path is part of the public agent integration surface.
---
